Package: ggblush
Type: Package
Title: Create Personalized Color Palettes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gregory P. Way
Maintainer: gregory.way@gmail.com
Description:
    Automatically generate color palettes using your favorite pictures.
    ggblush can be used with ggplot2 to use customized colors when generating publication-ready figures.
    Provide a filename or image url to extract beautiful colors.
License: BSD-3-Clause
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
